under this Act, a strata corporation has the power and capacity of a natural person of full capacity.</bcl:text></bcl:subsection></bcl:section><bcl:section id="d2e755"><bcl:marginalnote>Responsibilities of strata corporation</bcl:marginalnote><bcl:num>3</bcl:num><bcl:text>Except as otherwise provided in this Act, the strata corporation is responsible for managing and maintaining the common property and common assets of the strata corporation for the benefit of the owners.</bcl:text></bcl:section><bcl:section id="d2e767"><bcl:marginalnote>Strata corporation functions through council</bcl:marginalnote><bcl:num>4</bcl:num><bcl:text>The powers and duties of the strata corporation must be exercised and performed by a council, unless this Act, the regulations or the bylaws provide otherwise.</bcl:text></bcl:section></bcl:part></act:content><bcl:multinav><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Contents</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_00</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 1</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_01</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage currpage="true"><bcl:navtitle>Part 2</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_02</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 3</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_03</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 4</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_04</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 5</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_05</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 6</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_06</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 7</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_07</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 8</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_08</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 9</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_09</bcl:navxmlfile></bcl:navpage><bcl:navpage><bcl:navtitle>Part 10</bcl:navtitle><bcl:navxmlfile>98043_10</bcl:navxmlfile></